#ROOM
Vnum     22100
Name     &rThe Gates of Stratholme&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The high stone walls of Stratholme loom over you, eternally 
shrouded in the smoke of the burning city. A massive iron gate 
marks the entrance to the once-great northern hub. The air is 
thick with the scent of burning flesh and the sulfurous gas of 
the plague. A shimmering white portal glows within the main 
archway, leading into the city's cursed interior.
~
#EXIT
Direction out~
ToRoom    38563
Desc      Return to the Eastern Plaguelands.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    22101
Desc      The Entry Square.~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     22101
Name     &rThe Entry Square&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A large stone square filled with overturned wagons and the 
skeletal remains of horses. To the west, the city streets lead 
toward the Scarlet bastion. To the east, a wide thoroughfare 
leads toward the undead quarter. High above, the necropolis 
of Naxxramas casts a permanent shadow over the square.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    22100
Desc      The entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    22102
Desc      Toward King's Square.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    22140
Desc      Toward Elders' Square.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 22019 10 22101
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     22102
Name     &rThe Burning Way - West&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The houses on both sides of the street are eternally burning, 
the flames fed by necromantic magic. Skeletal citizens 
wander the center of the road, their eyes glowing with 
madness. To the north, a small alleyway leads toward 
the city's post office.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    22101
Desc      The entry square.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    22103
Desc      King's Square.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    22108
Desc      Toward the Post Office.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 22019 10 22102
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     22103
Name     &rKing's Square - Entrance&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A massive circular plaza that was once the pride of the city. 
A high stone fountain in the center is filled with blood, 
and the air is thick with the cries of restless souls. 
Timmy the Cruel can often be seen prowling the square.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    22102
Desc      The burning way.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    22104
Desc      Deep into King's Square.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    22115
Desc      Toward Crusader's Square.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 22011 1 22103
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     22104
Name     &rKing's Square - Central&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The heart of the western city. Shattered buildings line the 
square, and the central fountain overflows with stagnant 
darkness. Rockwing gargoyles watch from the high roofs, 
ready to dive on anyone who enters the plaza.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    22103
Desc      The entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    22105
Desc      Toward the Festival Lane.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 22017 10 22104
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     22105
Name     &rFestival Lane - Entrance&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A narrow, festive street that has been turned into a scene 
of carnage. Colorful banners, now tattered and grey, hang 
from the houses.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    22104
Desc      King's Square.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    22106
Desc      The Festival Lane Center.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 22035 10 22105
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     22106
Name     &rFestival Lane - Heart&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The deepest part of the lane. A large bonfire burns in the 
middle of the street, fueled by the remains of the city's 
furniture.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    22105
Desc      The lane entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset O 0 22054 10 22106
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     22108
Name     &rThe Post Office - Entrance&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A small, well-built stone building. Several blue-painted 
mailboxes stand outside, though they have been dented 
and stained with rust. The sound of a ringing bell 
echoes from within.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    22102
Desc      The burning way.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    22109
Desc      The Sorting Room.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 22010 1 22108
  Reset G 1 22045 1
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     22109
Name     &rThe Sorting Room&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     Crates and sacks of undelivered mail are piled to the 
ceiling. Restless souls of former couriers wander the 
room, attempting to complete their final deliveries.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    22108
Desc      The entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 22023 10 22109
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     22110
Name     &rKing's Square Overflow A&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A quiet corner of the plaza filled with overturned carts 
and the smell of old ozone.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    22103
Desc      The entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 22016 5 22110
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     22115
Name     &rThe Road to the Bastion - Entrance&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The road becomes wider and more organized as you approach the 
Scarlet territory. The burning buildings are replaced by 
stone barricades and bright red banners. Scarlet 
defenders stand guard at every intersection.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    22103
Desc      King's Square.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    22116
Desc      Crusader's Square.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 22038 5 22115
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     22116
Name     &rCrusader's Square&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The heart of the Scarlet Crusade's operations in Stratholme. 
The square is impeccably clean, and the air is clear of 
the plague-smoke. A grand cathedral stands on the north 
side of the plaza, its white stone reflecting the pale sky.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    22115
Desc      The road entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    22117
Desc      The Scarlet Bastion Entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    22125
Desc      Toward the Cannon Master's Lair.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 22012 10 22116
Reset O 0 22055 5 22116
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     22117
Name     &rThe Scarlet Bastion - Entrance&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A grand hall with high, vaulted ceilings. The floor is 
polished marble and the walls are draped in fine red 
silks. Scarlet centurions stand in silent vigil at the 
main archway.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    22116
Desc      The square.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    22118
Desc      The Hall of Valour.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 22012 5 22117
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     22118
Name     &rThe Hall of Valour&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A wide thoroughfare filled with statues of the Crusade's 
greatest heroes. To the east lies the city's archive, 
while to the west, a high bridge leads toward the 
Commander's private quarters.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    22117
Desc      The entrance hall.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    22119
Desc      The Archivist's Office.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    22121
Desc      The Grand Crusader's Throne.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 22022 5 22118
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     22119
Name     &rThe Archivist's Office&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A large room overflowing with maps, scrolls, and ancient 
books. Archivist Galford stands before a massive, 
burning fireplace, tossing handfuls of parchment 
into the flames.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    22118
Desc      The hall of valour.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 22009 1 22119
  Reset G 1 22047 1
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     22120
Name     &rThe Bastion Archive&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors dark~
Desc     A small, subterranean room beneath the archivist's office. 
It contains the few texts that Galford deemed "pure" 
enough to survive.
~
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    22119
Desc      Return to the office.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset O 0 22051 1 22120
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     22121
Name     &rThe Throne of Grand Crusader Dathrohan&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The highest point of the Scarlet Bastion. Grand Crusader 
Dathrohan sits upon a high throne, his armor gleaming 
with an unnatural red light. He oversees the final 
purification of Stratholme with eyes full of hidden 
malice.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    22118
Desc      The hall of valour.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    22122
Desc      Toward the Balnazzar Chamber.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 22001 1 22121
  Reset E 1 22073 1 16
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     22122
Name     &rThe Chamber of Balnazzar&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A dark, ominous room hidden behind the throne. In the 
center, the dreadlord Balnazzar has shed his human 
skin, his massive wings fanned as he drinks in the 
shadowy energy of the mountain.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    22121
Desc      The throne room.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 22002 1 22122
  Reset G 1 22048 1
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     22123
Name     &rThe Bastion Side-wing&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A quiet hallway in the back of the bastion, used by 
the Crimson Conjurers to study their spells.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    22118
Desc      The hall of valour.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 22013 10 22123
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     22124
Name     &rBastion Overflow A&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A side room filled with Headmaster's Charge-staves and 
ancient Lordaeron coins.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    22118
Desc      The hall of valour.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset O 0 22055 10 22124
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     22125
Name     &rThe Arsenal of Willey&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A massive iron chamber housing the city's heavy cannons. 
Cannon Master Willey stands near a pile of black-powder 
barrels, his fuse already lit. The air is thick with 
the scent of grease and charcoal.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    22116
Desc      Return to the square.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 22008 1 22125
  Reset G 1 22046 1
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     22126
Name     &rThe Smithy of the Crusade&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A large stone forge where the Crimson Hammersmiths 
work. The sound of hammering is constant, and the 
room is blistering hot.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    22116
Desc      The square.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 22025 5 22126
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     22140
Name     &rElders' Square - Entrance&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The start of the undead territory. The architecture here 
is noticeably more decayed, with bones and mummified 
remains used as building materials. Magistrate 
Barthilas can often be seen patrolling the entrance.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    22101
Desc      The entry square.~
