#ROOM
Vnum     22141
Name     &rElders' Square - Central&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A wide plaza filled with ancient ziggurats. Each ziggurat 
is guarded by a powerful Scourge champion. The air 
is absolute still and freezing cold.
~
